   _NMR_STAR_version        2.1.1
   _Experimental_method     NMR
   _Details                
;
Chemical shifts of full length, wild-type HIV-1 capsid protein in tubular
assemblies formed under high ionic strength. Sequential assignments based on 2D
and 3D magic-angle spinning NMR spectra and automated resonance assignment using
the program MCASSIGN2.
;

